# Research Question
How does public transportation accessibility influence air quality dynamics across Paris over space and time?

## Data Sources

### Roads & Navigation
- Google Roads API: Maps GPS coordinates to the most probable road, identifies speed limits, and detects road segments.  
  [Roads API Documentation](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/roads/overview)

- Google Directions API: Provides route planning and navigation for multiple transport modes, including public transit, driving, and walking.  
  [Directions API Documentation](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/directions/overview)

### Environmental & Location Data
- Google Air Quality API: Retrieves real-time and historical air pollution data for global locations.  
  [Air Quality API Documentation](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/air-quality/overview)

- Google Places API: Supplies location-based data, including places, businesses, transit stations, and geographic details.  
  [Places API Documentation](https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/places/overview)

